{"tid":2051812,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"認真Post，呢度有冇Ching請文職？","createTime":"2020-06-05T05:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T12:27:07.000Z","uid":96501,"like":14,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2761c8b6aefc2cadb604d35a38f5b0e5751fa92d","tid":2051812,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"運動加埋疫情，做開嗰間公司三月接咗<br />\n成個三月四月五月到而家六月零收入<br />\nSend CV出去send咗二百份有多，<br />\n有Interview嘅一隻手數得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有儲開錢，但我係屋企唯一經濟支柱&hellip;<br />\n成三個幾月零收入，供樓水電煤管理費雜費每個月大大話話HKD 18,000走唔甩，<br />\n我今個月再搵唔到工，依家住緊嗰度要放盤，到時兩老加埋廢青細佬真係要瞓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到呢度我真係好想自殺&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n一直好想入一間start-up闖下，<br />\n因為自己本身性格係鍾意由零去創造一啲野，<br />\n即使低啲人工都唔緊要，<br />\n但而家呢個環境，有份工已經係萬幸。<br />\n<br />\n自問自己background同待人接物都唔錯，MBA BBA有齊，有around 4年list co FI back office經驗，如果有Ching / Ching公司請人，可唔可以幫下小弟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/dieblackcops\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdieblackcops&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Eq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=e00e799c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dieblackcops</a>"},{"pid":"b88fe337dfe14cc74204c59eddc247fa6b863ee9","tid":2051812,"uid":20241,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"小妹就請小弟不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4977365364e9ed02467eae7e7f82102921702d","tid":2051812,"uid":220359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"幫推，巴打希望在明天，咁高學歷實會有機會既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c245643e229c7eed0b8f0d40554910a47165902","tid":2051812,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"ching 兩日月前唔係有兩個offer?"},{"pid":"7bd5158c9